Package: incus-windows-toolkit
Architecture: all
Depends: bash (>= 4.0), curl, jq, ${misc:Depends}
Recommends: incus, qemu-utils, wimlib-tools, xorriso, freerdp2-x11 | freerdp3-x11
Suggests: dialog, hivex, cabextract, shellcheck
Description: Unified CLI for Windows VM management on Incus
 IWT handles the full Windows VM lifecycle on Incus: ISO download,
 image building with driver injection and debloating, VM creation
 from templates, guest tool installation, GPU/USB passthrough,
 shared folders, RemoteApp, snapshots, and backup/export.
 Supports x86_64 and ARM64.
